<HEADLINE>
<P>
WILSON SLOGAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I submit the following slogan to the Wilson Reelection Committee without 
charge: 
</P>
<P>
 "Three Browns and You're Out!" 
</P>
<P>
 STAN JOHNSTON 
</P>
<P>
 Hacienda Heights 
</P>
