<P>
BRIEFLY; REDEVELOPMENT: HEARING ON PLAN FOR WILMINGTON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SUSAN WOODWARD 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A plan to attract business and redevelop 230 acres in a light industrial area 
will be discussed at a public hearing Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 The Los Angeles Community Redevelopment Agency will present its five-year 
draft plan designed to revitalize the Wilmington Industrial Park, which is 
bordered by Broad Avenue, and Anaheim, B and Alameda streets. 
</P>
<P>
