<P>
 After watching all 24 World Cup teams play at least once, Blatter, general 
secretary of FIFA, said his favorites are Brazil and Nigeria. 
</P>
<P>
 "They are fast, confident and skillful," he said from his Cup headquarters in 
Irving, Tex. ELLIOTT ALMOND 
