<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Hal Steele has been appointed director of production for the Western regional 
office of Column Financial Inc. He will work in the Irvine office of the 
Atlanta-based commercial mortgage company. Steel was formerly a vice president 
for Travelers Realty Investment Co. and, before that, was regional vice 
president for Mutual of New York. 
</P>
