earn degrees from Whittier College and a doctorate in education from USC. 
</P>
<P>
 He has served as a teacher, administrator and coach for 38 years, including 24 
years as the county's superintendent of schools. In that role, Cowan worked 
closely with fair officials to ensure youth involvement, Raley said. 
</P>
<P>
 The Ventura County Fair parade will begin at 10 a.m. Saturday, Aug. 20. The 
parade will travel down Main Street from Catalina Street west to the San 
Buenaventura Mission. TRACY WILSON 
