in the top 15 after two rounds include Terry Noe (150) and John Park of 
Fullerton (151). Right behind are Benjamin Bost of Mission Viejo (152) and Ryan 
Donovan of Yorba Linda (152). 
</P>
<P>
 The tournament is for boys ages 15-18. 
</P>
