<HEADLINE>
<P>
1994 LOS ANGELES TIMES; ALL-VENTURA BASEBALL TEAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach: Richard Duran 
</P>
<P>
 School: RIO MESA 
</P>
<P>
 Duran guided Rio Mesa to the Channel League championship, a 21-7 record and a 
trip to the Southern Section Division II semifinals one year after the Spartans 
finished last in the league. 
</P>
<P>
 Student: Jason Adamson 
</P>
<P>
 School: MOORPARK 
</P>
<P>
 Position: OF 
</P>
<P>
 A 6-foot-3, 195-pound senior, Adamson helped Moorpark to the Frontier League 
championship. He hit .435 with four home runs and 24 RBIs. Adamson was a 
