<P>
 Student: Ray Clinton 
</P>
<P>
 School: NEWBURY PARK 
</P>
<P>
 Position: P 
</P>
<P>
 Clinton, the Marmonte League pitcher of the year, set a Newbury Park record 
for victories in a season by going 10-3 with a 1.41 ERA. He pitched a four-hit 
shutout against Hoover in his only playoff start. 
